dialogue.text: *Spidey then shot a magic enchanted web at Electro. Sending him to Strange's dungeon*
I can't believe you called me emotional support spidey.
No I didn't mean it like that, look what it did for you. You popped off.
So you are saying you just called me that.. to anger me?
I guess you could say that.. I kinda thought you were emotional support but look. You clearly are more then that.
well duh, she is my gf!
Well, we aren't done yet. We still gotta look for the flying green elf. I'm gonna go check on my Aunt May first. If you find him...-
scream as loud as you can.
